clude. For example, if you want an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNLineStyleLayer","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" object to display only important features, you might assign","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a value above 50 to the important features’ ","type":"text"},{"code":"importance","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" attribute, then set","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer\/predicate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" to an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/foundation\/nspredicate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" with the format","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"importance > 50","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can also configure many layout and paint attributes of an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyleLayer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object to match the value of an attribute in this dictionary whenever it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"renders this feature. For example, if you display features in an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" using an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCircleStyleLayer"},{"type":"text","text":", you can assign a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"halfway"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"attribute to each of the source’s features, then set"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCircleStyleLayer\/circleRadius"},{"type":"text","text":" to an expression for the key path "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"halfway"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/text"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/iconImageName"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties allow you to use attributes yet another way. For example, to label"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"features in an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" object by their names, you can assign a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"name"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"attribute to each of the source’s features, then set","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/text"},{"text":" to an expression for the constant string value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"{name}","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". See the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Predicates and Expressions","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"guide for more information about expressions.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In vector tiles loaded by ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource","isActive":true},{"text":" objects, the keys and values of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"each feature’s attribute dictionary are determined by the source. Each","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"attribute name is a string, while each attribute value may be a null value,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Boolean value, integer, floating-point number, or string. These data types are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"mapped to instances of the following Foundation classes:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In the tile source","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In this dictionary","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Null"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"NSNull","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"boolValue"},{"type":"text","text":" property)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSNumber"},{"type":"text","text":" (use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"unsignedLongLongValue"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"longLongValue"},{"type":"text","text":" property)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"number"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSNumber"},{"type":"text","text":" (use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"doubleValue"},{"type":"text","text":" property)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"String","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"NSString","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]]]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When adding a feature to an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":", use the same Foundation types","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"listed above for each attribute value. In addition to the Foundation types, you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"may also set an attribute to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSColor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (macOS) or ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIColor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (iOS), which","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"will be converted into its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"CSS string representation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when the feature is added to an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":". This can be convenient when","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"using the attribute to supply a value for a color-typed layout or paint","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"attribute via a key path expression.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that while it is possible to change this value on feature"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instances obtained from "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/visibleFeaturesAtPoint:","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and related"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"methods, there will be no effect on the map. Setting this value can be useful"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when the feature instance is used to initialize an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source is added to the map and styled."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature\/attributes"},"sections":[]